Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,========OPJP=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:03.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}泣きじゃくりながら旅をしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}せめてこの宇宙（そら）を飛べるのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:14.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喧嘩した夜は星が優しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:19.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}キミも見ているかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:25.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}シラナイ…シリタイ…カンジタイ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:32.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}なんにもないなら　なんにでもなれるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:36.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}その時 生まれたときめきが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:38.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}時空の波サーフしてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:44.13,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不思議だね　今なら怖くない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:47.05,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}未完成なまま　飛び込もう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}約束の扉（ドア）を開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:54.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}まぶしい笑顔になれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:03.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抽泣着走在旅途上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若至少要是能在这片宇宙中翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:14.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吵架后的夜晚繁星是如此温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:19.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是不是也在看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:25.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么都不知道…想要去了解…想要去感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:32.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果一无所有 那么反而能化身一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:36.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个时候心中的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:38.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乘着时空的巨浪飞了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:44.13,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真不可思议 现在的我无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:47.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保持不成熟的自己就这么冲过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打开那扇约定的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:54.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}露出耀眼的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:52.35,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}だって　顔を上げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:58.29,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}みんなが微笑んでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:07.66,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恥ずかしくて　嬉しくて 横向く星空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:17.17,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}あれから毎日がダメって思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:26.70,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}いま少し　ほんの少し 自分に聞いてみたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:28.09,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「飛べるかなぁ？」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:32.84,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}“そら”で逢おう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:38.09,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}わたしたちいつでもゆける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:48.13,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}風が星を蒔いて　ひかりが躍る彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:52.80,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}“つかまえなきゃ”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:23:02.29,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}その手をのばした瞬間に　ひろがる風景は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:07.48,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}ラリ　いつかのafter school
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:52.35,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为一抬起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:58.29,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家都在冲我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:07.66,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又害羞又高兴 转头朝向星空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:17.17,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自那之后每天都觉得自己办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:26.70,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在稍微 稍微试着 向自己发问
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:28.09,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}“我能飞了吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:32.84,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在“宇宙”相会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:38.09,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们随时都能前往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:48.13,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}风儿播种着繁星 发着光刮向悦动的远方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:52.80,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}“必须要抓住”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:23:02.29,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}眼前的风景随着伸出的手铺展开来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:07.48,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一闪而过 那曾几何时的放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.21,0:00:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么小葵在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么昴在这里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.19,0:00:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那身衣服很适合小葵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不坐巴士吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么问 倒是昴你不坐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我的座位哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是我的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 课桌不够了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底跑哪去了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小树
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是课桌不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是葵的座位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是昴的才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经你这么一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像又有这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里是我们的教室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 到昨天为止还…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,课桌 就用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪搬来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs98\b1\pos(960,750)\bord0}巡星之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么大家会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说的话应该是彼此彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我们也不是最开始就都在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每多一个人就会发生一次和刚才一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对 树会不知道从哪搬来课桌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重点不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每多 一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这次又不同以往了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊真是的 该怎么说明才好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要点名了哟 你们5个赶紧坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们关系真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始上课吧 大家把教科书翻到第98页
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人都不会在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天将会接着上周的内容继续讲解比例
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 看好黑板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 将会就比例的思考方法所必须的用语进行说明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会画图解 请大家仔细看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么到底是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将你们作为协助者召唤而来的的确是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是以我的力量本应该最多只能召唤出一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么？那么会长召唤的人到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事怎么可能会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真随便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还真是悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:05:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全因为你们不知道要召唤协助者是多么困难的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事更不可能会知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 这个是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天不是说过是外星人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 昴宿星团星人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,货 货真价实？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思议的事情都发生了那么多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人而已会出现的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浩瀚无限的巨大宇宙 就算遭遇机率再小也并非遇不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过昴会迟疑也不能怪她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我之前没有信心 但是通过昴和葵我得到了确信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你们五人会被选上 为什么会聚集于同一张课桌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 理科值日生 我要为下一堂课做准备 你也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我说你啊 你那身打扮不能想办法改改吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少改穿白色的如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说其他人看不到外星人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我们变身的时候普通人也是看不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被选上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎——像这样凹凸不平的海岸叫做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情要追溯到七年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你长话短说 否则午休都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你们没辙 一言蔽之的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在现在这个世界中你们每个人的命运线呈重叠在一起的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命运线？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个世界五个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也缩得太短了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 能让我过一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少昴和葵多少察觉到了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本应互相熟知的人却有着些许不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵你明明丢下我去了别的学校才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢！丢下我的难道不是昴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变成这样应该也跟我宇宙飞船所发生的故障有关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 事情这样那样地要追溯到七年前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这话留到下次再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来干吧 把碎片收集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来我们也能回到原本命运线了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常总是直到放学为止都避免不提那些的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟只会被当做怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要个能坐下来好好说话的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我来给你演示一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道传动轴的骑乘方法要怎么教会别人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什么 只要动起来就自然会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太熟练了都没法当做参考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶的基础是平衡感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带不了那么多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道能派上什么用场 不过好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 尽是那种胡来的方法根本当不了参考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没有教过别人的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就由葵来教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之实践出真知 提高负荷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我有在提高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不够 想象自己变成了天使 拍动起背后的白色羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天 天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到还挺少女的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要飞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像驾校似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要和小葵一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 至少小葵坐到前面来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:09:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们也出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有了点想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 光她们不跟来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可要加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬紧牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀呀 二位 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点飙过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你们去哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩尽自己的努力没少飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你们肯定饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小昴没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯 好像有点恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 昴你喜欢喝这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正大标宋_GBK\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H2601B6&\fs45\blur3\bord3\pos(906,160)\frz5.175}草莓牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小昴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样子不像是去厕所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs65\b1\bord2\blur10\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}瞭望室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭望室的钥匙 昨天忘记还了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来不怎么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个已经用不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？明明这么漂亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么问？你肯送我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为我已经不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:11:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为之前你看上去有点悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和久违的朋友相处得并不太顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明没有不想见面 明明见面会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太久没见反而没法好好说话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不希望改变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讨厌在你不知道的时候 熟悉的人变成了不熟悉的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说 不想改变的其实是你自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我也不太清楚朋友是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴为什么长着角？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊这个 因为怎么弄都会翘起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样很帅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想要改变也没有那么容易能改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能办到呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的朋友也是如此吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 既然如此变成朋友不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫凑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫昴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我再飞一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什么 昴认识的我 是个什么样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不用了 当我没问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 小葵认识的我 也是我不知道的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊 就算净是我所不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也庆幸能来到这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样对外星人会很失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一事归一事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集引擎碎片 当魔法使很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两者也并不冲突吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？小葵 那个星星是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也看了云层之上 那里本没有星星的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是超新星吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有变成魔法使的时候才能看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是会长口中的宇宙飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像那样绕着太阳周围在公转
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也像这样和小葵一起看星星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得我喜欢喝草莓牛奶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我高兴得都有点落泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是那样也用不着突然跑开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴果然是个爱哭鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花了一周时间终于取得临时驾照了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行的基本是速度和高度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提高高度就会降低速度 反之亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:15:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 还要继续吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然会降速但是高度得以爬升 这就是殷麦曼回旋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殷 殷麦曼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是上手不少了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯 因为没有慌张所以才勉强做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也不会迎合我们这边的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下就来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是飞机吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像变光星似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当快呢 有平常的一倍以上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过红移
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要等小葵和小昴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会飞远的 就我们几个试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不能令其简并 说不定也能停下它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面迎上让人有点怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传动轴追不上的话也只能这样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得有点奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 有两个？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分离了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 变成两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 昴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子两个这种事也会出现吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第一次 不过老是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵你听得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去像一个 但其实是两个碎片重叠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在虽然两个都简并了 但还没有完全停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互之间的引力和离心力处于平衡状态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果其中一边失去了力 两者的引力就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两边都会弹飞出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单说来是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说必须正正好好同时将两个碎片停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 殷麦曼回旋 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 还记得那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝎子红着眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊… 嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌张哦 昴 冷静地上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵才是 一个人做的了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你一个人还没成功过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把我当笨蛋 昴你也不过是一半靠的运气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我也…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是我认识的那个昴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们打算干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝎子红着眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄鹰高展翅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青眼睛的是小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盘身发光的是蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猎人高声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霜与露降临
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全一致！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片互相吸引的力量没有消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和刚才说的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事也会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有离心力消失了 一下子聚到一块去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 爬升
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 利用高度来降速
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来？这次是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了吧 这是我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算对昴做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋又出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 昴？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在等我们抓住碎片啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你们我随时随地随便就能占得先机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个碎片总有一天我也会收下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪我做得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭那么伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样都把我们那不甘给哭走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那家伙下次再出现 我也会保护好昴的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹得到了一个碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也并非都是让人扫兴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚重振好精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天起这里就是我们的房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是趁小葵和小昴在特训时我们在忙活的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是场漫长的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可费了不少苦心哦？
