Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,COSPLAY研究会？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我们五个就是部员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.20,0:22:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及会长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 COSPLAY什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.41,0:22:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也并非空穴来风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也没料到能这么快就拿到活动室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 不知道是不是该说运气好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 给
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:22:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
